### What Changed vs Your Original YAML

| What | Old | New |
|---|---|---|
| Composer download path | `/tools/composer/composer.phar` ❌ (didn't exist) | `/download/composer.phar` ✅ (proxied from getcomposer.org) |
| curl flag | no `-f` | added `-f` so curl fails on HTTP errors instead of saving error JSON |
| URL variables | hardcoded inline | extracted to `variables` block for maintainability |
| Everything else | unchanged | unchanged |

